Description:
Fresh & Tidy In A Sought-After Estate
Near-new and full of appeal, this modern 4-bedroom family home is located in the fantastic Parks Edge Estate amongst all that Cranbourne East has to offer!
Enjoy an active lifestyle with easy access to Casey RACE and Casey Fields sporting complex, as well as Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre, local schools and so much more.
This bright layout features a large spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry and a wide island benchtop overlooking open plan living and meals areas all extending out to a cosy covered patio for alfresco entertaining.
The master bedroom is privately positioned at the front of the home with its own ensuite and walk-in wardrobe, while the 3 additional bedrooms include built-in wardrobes and are serviced by a central bathroom with a separate toilet and laundry.
Landscaped front and rear yards keep this 325m2 block neat and tidy, with the remote lock-up double garage providing both rear and internal access to the home.
This is an ideal choice for first home buyers and those looking for low maintenance living, while the astute investor can take advantage of a month to month lease at $420 per week.
Contact Peter Demos 0490 051 760 to find out more about this property!
Features
- Ducted Heating
- Split System Air Con
- Plenty Of Storage Throughout
Upside Contact-Free Policy
Upside Contact-Free Policy
- Private inspections are now allowed with one agent and one prospective purchaser. The prospective purchaser may be accompanied by one other person from an existing household or their partner, and the prospective purchaser's children (under 18 years old).
- Inspections are limited to 15 minutes and hand sanitiser will be provided.
- You cannot travel between Melbourne and regional Victoria for property inspections

Description:
Substantial Living in The Hunt Club!
Substantial family living in the prime location of Cranbourne East.
This expansive home proudly sits on an amazing 736m2(approx.) block and will comfortably accomodate a large family.
Positioned in the ever popular Hunt Club Estate only a short distance to Cranbourne East Primary and Secondary schools, Casey Grammar, Hunt Club Village Shopping Centre, public transport and local amenities.
Offering multiple lounge areas and extensive alfresco this home is perfect for entertaining.
The kitchen provides tremendous storage and bench space, gas cooktop, wall oven and dish-draw dishwasher, whilst being the central point of the home connecting the family & meals area. Ideal for family gatherings there is room for everyone with the adjoining rumpus and formal living & dining areas. Not to mention the generous alfresco area will perfectly accomodate all your summer BBQ's.
The master bedroom is privately placed at the front of the property with a spacious double vanity ensuite and walk-in robe.
The further 3 bedrooms situated to the rear of the home include built-in robes, ceiling fans and share the main bathroom and powder room.
Other features include:
- Ducted heating
- Evaporative Cooling
- Laundry with storage and external access
- Tripe car garage plus work/ storage space & rear roller door
- Ceiling fans
- Quality drapes
- Tile and laminate flooring
This home has so much to offer you must see it for yourself!

211.69m²

Description:
STUNNING VALUE - $560,000 - $610,000
STYLE & SOPHISTICATION
Introducing 42 Adrian Street, Cranbourne East. The perfect home for those with a taste for the finer things in life! Complete with high end finishes throughout this property will not disappoint even the most fastidious buyers.
Upon arrival you're immediately greeted by the ultra modern facade proudly sitting on a lovely low maintenance corner block.
Entering the front door you'll begin to notice the upgrades right away with raised ceiling height, the front formal lounge to the right, a stylish timber staircase and elegant tiling choices that lead into the the kitchen, dining and main living area. The kitchen is one that certainly ticks the boxes! Complete with beautiful caeserstone counter tops, under-mount double sink, 900mm gas cooker, a huge pantry and loads of other storage options. The main living area is sizeable enough for your choice of furniture options and opens up via the extra high stacker door onto the rear yard. Also featured downstairs is a powder room with external caeserstone vanity.
Moving upstairs we find 4 generously sized bedrooms including the master with walk in robe and an extremely high-class ensuite featuring oversized shower & caeserstone vanity while the further 3 bedrooms are all fitted with built in robes and serviced by the family bathroom that again has a sophisticated modern style.
Further features of the home include: Gas ducted heating on both levels, ducted refrigerated cooling on both levels, double glazed windows, water tank, extra wide and extra high double remote garage with rear roller door access and much much more!
Just a stones throw to Casey fields sporting complex, Casey RACE, a variety of schools (both secondary and primary), public transport & shopping centres this home still has a nice sense of privacy being tucked away in a quiet corner of Cranbourne East.
Its all here and it won't last long! Call today to arrange an inspection!!
COVID-19 NOTICE: Following current guidelines, we ask that any attendee to the property please wear a mask at all times. We will provide you with hand sanitiser prior to entering the property & upon leaving the home. We ask that you please adhere to the current social distancing rules while inspecting the property, and please refrain from touching any surfaces within the home. If you are unwell, or have been in contact with someone who is unwell, we ask that you please do not attend the inspection, and instead we can assist you with a virtual tour of the property. Thank you for your cooperation.

Description:
Sleek, Contemporary Style in the Livingston Estate
Primed for immediate family enjoyment opposite a children's playground, this glorious Livingston Estate residence has been sleekly designed with careful consideration given to its low-maintenance lifestyle agenda.
- Four robed bedrooms including a master suite with walk-through-robe to stylish ensuite, supplemented by a family bathroom, separate toilet and full-sized laundry
- Taking pride of place at the front of the home, the lounge room is enriched with plush carpeting underfoot
- Awash with glorious sunshine due to its northerly orientation, the open plan kitchen, meals and family room incorporates stone benchtops, 900mm stainless steel appliances, soft-close cabinetry and a convenient breakfast bench
- Stunning porcelain tiles flow throughout, accompanied with carpeting to all bedrooms
- Compact rear yard offers the ideal space for outdoor relaxation or as a terrific play space for children
- Ducted heating, evaporative cooling, Colorbond fence plus double garage with internal access
Presenting the perfect setting to inspire happy family memories, within walking distance to Casey Fields Primary, Cranbourne Secondary, Casey Grammar, Casey RACE & Casey Fields sporting facilities & Cranbourne Shopping Centre, close to trains plus major road arterials.

Description:
WHAT DREAMS ARE MADE OF
CRANBOURNE EAST: Set on a block of approximately 375 SQMS is this massive opportunity to secure the best home in the best street in Cranbourne East. Its location is second to none and the amenities around this home is a purchasers delight. Schools, play grounds, sports fields, shopping, etc you wouldn't fall short of any.
With a lovely facade up the front and well cared for front yard, you will be mesmerized the moment you step into this home. The grand entrance leads you along a walkway with the master bedroom located to the left of the home which comes with a FES and a WIR.
As you progress through the walkway you are then greeted by this amazing open plan kitchen, dining and family living area. The kitchen is so modern its a chef's delight, with plenty of counter top space, Caesar stone bench tops, a lot of storage, quality appliances, free standing oven, range hood, dishwasher, large fridge cavity with plumbing connected.
The open plan dining and family living area is spacious and overlooks the kitchen which is so ideal when entertaining. The remaining two robed bedrooms are situated to the left of the home alongside the master bedroom and well-serviced by the family shower and toilet.
If entertaining is your forte then the attached alfresco with access from the living zone is a must see. With mature plants, an awesome water feature and deck lights, its just such a tranquil setting to come to after a tiring day.
All of this and a lot more on 375 SQMS, you will surely be spoilt for choice

Description:
GREAT FAMILY HOME CLOSE TO SHOPS!
Presenting a wonderful 4 bedroom family home with 2 living areas close to Hunt Club shops, all set on a generous 569sqm block that faces north in a lovely tree lined street.
Upon entering the home, you are greeted with the large formal lounge, floating floors & tiling, with the home being freshly painted. The great sized master bedroom features an ensuite & walk in robe.
Heading through to the next zone is the light filled kitchen with updated appliances including gas cooking, oven & dishwasher, along with plenty of bench & cupboard space, all while overlooking the dining area & family room. There is ducted heating and evaporative cooling for your year round comfort.
At the rear of the home, three more bedrooms all have built in robes, while the neat family bathroom with separate toilet is nearby. With sliding cavity doors, this home is able to be zoned off to give all the family their private space.
Heading outside you have a large yet low maintenance backyard for the family or pets to enjoy, and rear roller door access from the double garage onto the spacious concreted area, perfect for entertaining or vehicle storage.
Set in the much loved Hunt Club estate within walking distance to the Hunt Club shops and close proximity to the Springhill shops, Cranbourne Centro, Cranbourne East Primary & Secondary schools, Casey Grammar, Marnebek, public transport, arterial roads and more, the location is ideal for families & investors and should be at the top of your shortlist. Call Daniel today!

Description:
Where Location Matters!!!
In the heart of modern Livingston Estate of Cranbourne East we present to you this great functional home that is sure to tick all the boxes for a growing family, first home buyers and investors.
This home features a beautiful facade that opens to a wide long hallway entrance. The master is at the front of the home with a walk in robe and en-suite. Complimented by two other bedrooms with built in robes, central bathroom are separate and well zoned ensuring privacy and space. Well appointed kitchen with glass splash back, stone bench and quality stainless steel appliances adjoining the family living and dining area.
Separate Theatre room is the perfect bonus this home offers as it can be used as a 2nd living space or converted into a 4th spacious bedroom.
Step outside the backyard and be met by an outdoor tiled and under roof line entertaining area perfect for all year round Melbourne weather.
Other features include ducted heating, reverse cycle air conditioning, security cameras, security alarm, garden shed, garage storage shelving, recycled water plus lots more.
This home will take the hassle away from building.
Located only moments from the new Casey Fields Primary school, Kindergarten, Casey Fields sports clubs and recreation parks, Casey RACE Recreation and Aquatic Centre, Schools, Shopping and easy access to freeways.

Description:
Lifestyle and Community
Contact agent for private viewing!
Welcome to your new contemporary 4 bedroom plus Study home in the sought-after Cranbourne East's Livingston Estate. Walking distance to nearby childcare center, shops, parks and public transport.
Offering a welcoming street presence and a prized location that is close to local amenities and services, this Boutique Winchester 28 home by Metricon has it all, class, quality and position.
The owners have spared no expense to present a luxurious and inviting home with many modern features to offer you a stylish living experience in this community strong Estate.
Complete with an abundance of rear yard this low maintenance landscaped 448m² allotment offer so much more combined with multiple living zones your new home will be the place to be for get-togethers and parties.
Upon entering, you're met with the highest quality living featuring neutral and soft tones, walking through the home past the formal lounge and into the open plan kitchen/butler's pantry , family, living highlighted by a well-positioned gas log fireplace and you'll be amazed at the space it has to offer.
Upstairs an impressive master bedroom with heating/cooling, a full ensuite with a separate toilet, a massive shower, and a WIR big enough for both his and her clothes!
Downstairs, boasting high ceilings of 2.7m, open the glass doors and embrace the gentle breezes by seamlessly blending outdoors and indoors. Outdoors featuring a blooming citrus garden.
The remaining bedrooms are big enough to fit queen-sized beds, and all have built-in robes.
Inquires without mobiles will not be returned

Description:
GRAND FAMILY LIVING
Grand family living in The Hunt Club.
A stunning spacious 5 bedroom home, beautifully presented and offering an abundance of space and entertaining options
Exceptional frontage with ample parking and curved driveway lined with established gardens provides privacy and appeal.
3 Superb living areas beautifully filled with natural light, including formal living and dining, separate family and central dining / pool room featuring the log fire to keep you warm and cosy throughout winter.
In addition the extensive undercover outdoor area can comfortably accomodate all your entertaining needs.
Be surrounded by family in your hostess kitchen appointed with quality granite bench tops, island bench with breakfast bar, stainless gas cook top, wall oven and dishwasher.
The master bedroom positioned at the at the front of the home, provides privacy and space fitted with walk-in robe and generous ensuite
4 additional bedrooms are all complete with built -in robes The 5th bedroom can also utilised as a study.
Other essential features include central heating and cooling, Tasmania Oak hardwood floors, feature floor tiling, generous laundry with storage and bench space, double garage with rear access roller door, large block 767m2(approx) low maintenance gardens and much much more.
Located within easy access of Cranbourne East primary and Secondary College, Early learning centre, Hunt Club Village Shopping Centre, walking tracks and parks. Ideally located close to public transport and links to major arterials.
This impressive home will tick all the boxes, call to arrange your inspection.
